graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.13+<br/>Routes, ServiceMonitors]
    DSPO -->|v2 execution| Argo[Argo Workflows 3.3.10<br/>Required for DSP v2]
    DSPO -->|v1 execution| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+<br/>Required for DSP v1]
    DSPO -->|upstream components| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>v2: 2.0.5<br/>v1: 1.5.1-tekton]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|optional DB| MariaDBExt[MariaDB 10.3<br/>Optional internal component]
    DSPO -.->|optional storage| MinioExt[Minio<br/>RELEASE.2019-08-14T20-37-41Z<br/>Optional internal component]
    DSPO -.->|optional metadata| MLMD[ML Metadata 1.14.0<br/>Optional for v2]
    DSPO -.->|optional proxy| Envoy[Envoy Proxy 1.22.11<br/>For MLMD gRPC]

    %% External Services (Alternative storage)
    DSPO -.->|alternative storage| ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>AWS/Compatible<br/>HTTPS/443]
    DSPO -.->|alternative DB| ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP]

    %% Infrastructure Services
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Token validation]
    DSPO -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Auto-rotating certs]
    DSPO -->|container images| Registry[Container Registries<br/>HTTPS/443]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|deployed by| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster CR]
    DSPO -.->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[odh-dashboard<br/>Pipeline UI access]

    %% Monitoring & Observability
    DSPO -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor scraping]
    DSPO -.->|optional mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh / Istio<br/>Optional mTLS]

    %% Kubernetes Core
    DSPO -->|API interactions| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>RBAC enforcement]

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    style OpenShift fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Argo fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Tekton fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style KFP fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    style MariaDBExt fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style MinioExt fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style MLMD fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Envoy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External Services
    style ExternalS3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Infrastructure
    style OAuth fill:#3498db,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#3498db,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#3498db,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#3498db,stroke:#333

    %% Internal ODH
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Monitoring
    style Prometheus fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ServiceMesh fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
